job.title: GAIL Officer & Executive Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for Various Vacancies in Gujarat
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Executive Trainee (Marketing)
  • Senior Officer / Officer (Marketing) 

Description

New Central Government Jobs have been published by the Gas Authority of India Limited for the vacancies of Executive Trainee. If you are finding a government job in Gujarat then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for these vacancies in Gujarat, from 18.05.2021, and till 30.05.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Gujarat and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification to apply for GAIL Executive Trainee posts in Gujarat:

  • To apply for an Executive Trainee post in Gujarat, your B.E/B.Tech, Degree, MBA must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these vacancies is the 18.05.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these vacancies is 30.05.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 40  years old. 

GAIL Executive Trainee Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for GAIL Officer & Executive Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process for these posts in Gujarat. Fill in your details and submit it

  • Or follow all the steps given below,
  •  First, go to the official website of GAIL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked BY GAIL.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
